registry/assessments/l3a-parse.json:63:    "cross_experiment_picture": "l3a-parse and a5-nl land exactly on the programme's most consistent measured pattern, and sharpen it with a NEW axis. The pattern [reading, EXTRAPOLATION per ASM-0721, never a premise]: the kernel's deterministic machinery keeps passing ON ITS OWN CLOSED GRAMMAR / self-authored substrate, while every measured attempt to cross a boundary into real or natural input fails or is inconclusive. On the machinery side: l3a-parse & a5-nl gold-replication identical (527/527 and 855/855 in-run), g8's F/B round-trip 33/33 with live F-verification, the parent engine exactness 100% on gold [MEASURED, each in its own verdict]. On the boundary side, the measured negatives now line up on FOUR distinct boundaries: (i) the NATURAL-LANGUAGE input boundary — l3a-parse 47.6% and a5-nl 41.6%, both FAIL the 0.90 bar (THIS pair); (ii) the WILD-FORMAL-CONTENT boundary — g8 fragment 0/1000 random Mathlib at kernel size 39 (FAIL, cross-vendor CONFIRMED); (iii) the MODEL-INTERNAL-COMPUTATION boundary — nsk1 flagship INCONCLUSIVE (the internal channel DELIVERS at echo grade but INTEGRATION into free generation is unresolved at-or-below the content-free null); (iv) the COMPUTE-MATCHED VERIFIER-OFFLOAD boundary — f2 FAIL (the kernel-verifier arm did not dominate the text null / gloss-self-verify at matched budget). g7 is a formalism-capacity design selection (kot-ast/2), not a boundary result; g9-llmproxy is an early-warning FAIL-analog on the authoring lane (claims paused, HS-A unadjudicated). The ONE PASS in the neighbourhood — truthstyle-2x2 — is explicitly an INSTRUMENT-adequacy result (LLM-judge endorsement is not materially style-leaky at margin 0.10), a supporting instrument fact that makes OTHER readings trustworthy, NOT a kernel-content win. The NEW axis this pair adds: the earlier boundary negatives were about whether the kernel CONTAINS the target (coverage — g8, m0b, compression-census). l3a-parse/a5-nl show that even for content the kernel DOES contain and CAN decide perfectly under gold parse, natural language cannot reliably ADDRESS it through the pinned deterministic front-end — a reachability boundary distinct from and stacked on top of the coverage boundary. Emerging correctness picture, stated as the evidence supports it and tagged: inside the fortress the deterministic machinery is exact and sound; every measured wall between that fortress and real input is real, and this pair measures the natural-language wall at ~42-48% reach [EXTRAPOLATION synthesis, ASM-0721; each figure index-bound to its own verdict's envelope; confirmed or broken only by the pre-registered per-boundary successors]."
